  "closed_at": "2016-05-19T05:27:16Z",
  "body": "e.g  **xtemplate**\n\n```\n{{set (array = [1,2,3])}}\n{{#each(array)}}\n<div class=\"{{if(xindex===array.length-1)}}last-child{{}}\"></div>\n{{/each}}\n\n```\n\nWell,I realize it in `javascript style` , that I make styles in the item of `array`.But I don't think it's the best way,and when the special style is a great many , it will look like not very nice . So how could you realize it in best practice?\n",
